As a Talent Acquisition Sr. Specialist you need to ensure that staffing needs are being met with a long-term strategy in mind. Also you have to devise and implement sourcing strategies, such as an employer branding initiative, to build pipelines for potential applicants. Create and implement end-to-end hiring processes to ensure a positive experience for candidates. Last but least to form close relationships with hiring managers to ensure clear expectations for candidates and interviewers.

